ticket_id = "VPN-ANOMALY-001"
title = "Impossible Travel Alert"
description = "CRITICAL: Credential Theft Suspected. An employee account has logged in from two different countries within minutes. This is physically impossible.\n\n[b]Instruction:[/b] Use the SIEM to compare the two login IPs. Identify the malicious IP (the one from Tokyo) and type it into the [b]Root Cause[/b] box to flag the account for review."
